      "code": "def normalize(s):\n    # remove diacritics\n    s=''.join(c for c in s if unicodedata.category(c)!='Mn')\n    # remove tatweel\n    s=s.replace('ـ','')\n    # unify hamza forms?\n    repl={'أ':'ا','إ':'ا','آ':'ا','ٱ':'ا','ؤ':'و','ئ':'ي','ة':'ه','ى':'ي','ٰ':''}\n    for k,v in repl.items():\n        s=s.replace(k,v)\n    # remove punctuation\n    s=re.sub(r'[^\\w\\s]+',' ',s)\n    s=re.sub(r'\\s+',' ',s).strip()\n    return s\ntarget_full=\"وَمَن يُشَاوِرْكُمُ فِي الْحَيَاةِ الدُّنْيَا فَسَوْفَ يَرُدُّكُمْ إِلَى الْقِيَامَةِ ثُمَّ يُنَبِّئُكُم بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَعْمَلُونَ\"\nnorm_target=normalize(target_full)\nnorm_target",
      "container_id": "cntr_6896726f69848190a0e732922012bf1b0a53da12dad10396",
      "outputs": null,
      "status": "completed",
